Feature: commitment
	As a user
	I want to be able commit to buying items in the shopping list
	so the group can collective decide if the item should be purchased 

	Scenario: Initially an item has 0 commitments and is labeled 'intent'
	Scenario: A user can click 'commit' to register their commitment to an item
	Scenario: An item is labeled 'commited' when the majority of the group has commited to the item
